text: Catherine Elizabeth "Cat" Deeley (born 23 October 1976) is an English television presenter, model, actress, and television personality who is currently hosting This Morning with Ben Shephard since March 2024. From 1998 to 2002, she hosted the children's programme SMTV Live and its spin-off chart show CD:UK. Deeley became the last presenter of Stars In Their Eyes.
